{"type": "article", "id": 3225, "title": "可拆卸的板凳", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-03T08:17:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232855m4Uj0kMLVplCEhOD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为 Yodessa 的凳子是新加坡设计工作室 Tizumuka 的作品，由塑料凳面、实木凳腿以及阀门旋钮三个独立的物件组合而成。组装时，使用者无需借助任何其他道具，白色塑料圆形凳面下面有四个圆形的小插孔，两个板凳腿可以交叉套在插孔里面，然后将阀门旋钮穿过凳腿横梁与凳面的螺丝孔拧紧，一款时尚的小凳子便组装完成了。Yodessa 的优势在于从运输、存储到组装各个环节的便利性，它还收获了今年的德国红点奖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232852fpbQiH2eLaWGXV1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232853HnBVMUb4JXA8FG67.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232853u7XJMVfjKx1L6OUF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232854OWTUjQmP0yF2kiA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}